BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 217.68 740 Td (WHAT IS HEALTH ANXIETY?) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 50 730 m 562 730 l S Q
BT 0 g /F1 11 Tf 50 705 Td (Health anxiety \(formerly hypochondria/Illness Anxiety Disorder\) is:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 11 Tf 50 685 Td (An intense fear that you have or will develop a serious illness,) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 11 Tf 50 665 Td (despite medical reassurance that you're healthy.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 12 Tf 50 635 Td (COMMON PATTERNS:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 615 Td (- Googling symptoms repeatedly) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 599 Td (- Checking body for signs of illness) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 583 Td (- Seeking reassurance from doctors/loved ones) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 567 Td (- Avoiding medical info OR obsessively consuming it) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 551 Td (- Interpreting normal body sensations as dangerous) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 535 Td (- Believing the worst-case scenario is happening) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 519 Td (- Brief relief after reassurance, then anxiety returns) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 50 493 Td (Which patterns do I relate to?) Tj ET
